textTemplates.name: thankYouLabelTextTemplate
textTemplates.text:
Thank you for your time! We'd like to remind you that we have a dedicated support email and phone number to reach our team at. Please don't hesitate to reach out to anchorsupport@bluewavesolar.com or 844-389-9780 if you have any questions. 


You will receive a separate email with a link to donate $25 to the charity of your choice!
